snippet.title: PVKII Map Update 2.6 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for the free game Pirates, Vikings, and Knights II Map Update 2.6. Update available October 31, 2013.
Video: Kyle Carter  |  Music: Bregan Mencarini

Visit http://www.pvkii.com for more information.
